WEBVTT

00:11.270 --> 00:12.160
Remember?

00:13.560 --> 00:15.290
When my father was still alive,

00:15.510 --> 00:16.770
you were his favorite.

00:17.000 --> 00:20.600
Whenever he came to the capital
for an audience with the emperor,

00:20.920 --> 00:22.720
he would stay at Qingshan Manor.

00:22.870 --> 00:25.440
Then we'd go hunting together
in the woods behind the mountain

00:25.440 --> 00:27.640
and make stew with the pheasants
we caught.

00:27.640 --> 00:28.670
Back then,

00:29.640 --> 00:30.700
my father even said

00:31.190 --> 00:33.710
he wanted to take you to the black forests
in Great Yan

00:33.710 --> 00:36.350
to hunt the golden pheasants
unique to our land.

00:36.350 --> 00:37.520
Now, it seems

00:38.880 --> 00:40.680
you will never visit my country.

00:41.750 --> 00:42.920
So, have a taste of it

00:43.640 --> 00:44.790
here instead.

00:50.920 --> 00:51.640
What?

00:52.100 --> 00:53.600
Afraid I've poisoned it?

01:14.640 --> 01:16.760
There's indeed no poison in this soup.

01:16.760 --> 01:20.310
But it contains mirabilite, an extremely
cold-natured herb, and pinellia.

01:20.310 --> 01:22.510
These would aggravate my hypothermia.

01:24.039 --> 01:25.440
You're overthinking it.

01:26.950 --> 01:29.590
These are just ordinary herbs used
when stewing golden pheasants.

01:29.590 --> 01:31.320
The bird is highly nourishing,

01:31.350 --> 01:34.009
so it must be balanced with
cold-natured herbs.

01:35.640 --> 01:36.840
And that's not all.

01:37.840 --> 01:40.200
You came here pretending to
form an alliance with Ximeng

01:40.200 --> 01:43.200
while secretly sending men
to the Black River Valley

01:44.759 --> 01:47.560
to gather information
about the black gold mines.

03:19.940 --> 03:25.230
[REBIRTH]

03:25.810 --> 03:28.300
[Episode 31]

03:29.680 --> 03:30.800
I forgot.

03:32.400 --> 03:34.530
You're the best spy of Qingshan Manor.

03:34.840 --> 03:36.360
Naturally, my tricks

03:36.870 --> 03:38.310
are nothing in your eyes.

03:38.960 --> 03:39.630
Otherwise,

03:41.360 --> 03:43.310
my family of 16

03:44.430 --> 03:47.160
wouldn't have died
on Jiuyou Platform back then!

03:47.280 --> 03:47.870
You...

03:49.470 --> 03:51.560
were once the friend I trusted most.

03:52.190 --> 03:53.190
There's one thing

03:55.470 --> 03:57.670
I need you to answer with your own mouth.

04:00.030 --> 04:03.160
The catastrophe that befell
my entire family back then—

04:03.910 --> 04:05.470
was it because of

04:06.840 --> 04:07.870
you?

04:12.280 --> 04:13.080
Your Majesty.

04:19.240 --> 04:20.829
These are the secret letters
Yan Shicheng sent

04:20.829 --> 04:23.360
to the feudal princes,
plotting a rebellion?

04:23.430 --> 04:24.040
Yes.

04:24.480 --> 04:25.240
I believe...

04:25.240 --> 04:26.240
As I expected.

04:26.800 --> 04:29.600
I've long suspected Yan Shicheng
of harboring treasonous ambitions,

04:29.600 --> 04:33.130
given how he's been consolidating
military power in the north.

04:33.159 --> 04:36.220
I believe these secret letters
are highly suspicious.

04:36.220 --> 04:37.900
What do you mean?

04:38.920 --> 04:41.159
I've privately investigated
these feudal princes.

04:41.159 --> 04:43.360
None of them has ever had
any dealings with Yan Shicheng.

04:43.360 --> 04:45.060
Among them, the Marquis of Zhennan
and the Prince of Huai'an

04:45.060 --> 04:47.320
actually have close ties with Lord Muhe.

04:47.680 --> 04:48.720
Furthermore, the territory
of the Prince of Huaixi

04:48.720 --> 04:50.190
lies far from Great Yan.

04:50.270 --> 04:52.190
Judging from the viable military routes,

04:52.190 --> 04:54.000
if Yan Shicheng truly intended to rebel,

04:54.000 --> 04:56.000
he wouldn't seek allies so far away.

04:56.000 --> 04:57.680
Great Yan is the military shield
of our state.

04:57.680 --> 04:59.270
Several powerful noble clans

04:59.270 --> 05:01.330
at court have long coveted that fief.

05:01.600 --> 05:02.800
We must proceed with caution.

05:02.800 --> 05:03.270
Enough.

05:03.430 --> 05:05.090
The evidence is already here.

05:05.120 --> 05:06.580
I'll make my own judgment.

05:06.950 --> 05:08.680
You need not concern yourself.

05:11.000 --> 05:13.130
It's not that Great Yan wants to rebel—

05:13.720 --> 05:16.120
it's that Your Majesty wants it to.

05:17.240 --> 05:19.000
Great Yan commands the Black Eagle Army
of 100,000 troops,

05:19.000 --> 05:20.530
half of them elite cavalry.

05:21.430 --> 05:23.760
Even if Yan Shicheng doesn't rebel today,

05:23.870 --> 05:25.040
there is no guarantee

05:25.040 --> 05:27.300
he won't have the heart to do so tomorrow.

05:30.830 --> 05:31.630
Your Majesty,

05:31.630 --> 05:33.360
Great Yan is the shield of our state.

05:33.360 --> 05:34.390
For so many years, Yan Shicheng

05:34.390 --> 05:35.950
has guarded the northern borders for us.

05:35.950 --> 05:36.880
I'm worried that

05:37.240 --> 05:39.480
if we condemn them
based on false evidence,

05:39.480 --> 05:41.920
they will turn against us
and fight with nothing left to lose,

05:41.920 --> 05:43.190
and the northern borders
will fall into chaos.

05:43.190 --> 05:45.920
That's why I'll summon him to the capital

05:46.070 --> 05:47.800
for an audience.

05:47.800 --> 05:50.240
Keep these secret letters hidden for now.

05:50.800 --> 05:53.240
We'll strike once he's here.

05:57.070 --> 05:57.800
Zhuge Yue,

05:59.390 --> 06:01.520
do you know how many people in the court

06:01.680 --> 06:04.390
have wanted to uproot Qingshan Manor
over the years

06:04.390 --> 06:06.920
and replace your grandfather,
Zhuge Muqing?

06:07.480 --> 06:10.830
And yet, why has no one ever succeeded?

06:11.950 --> 06:13.750
That's because Zhuge Muqing

06:13.870 --> 06:16.270
knows all the secrets of this country

06:16.680 --> 06:19.010
yet also knows
when to know nothing at all.

06:19.630 --> 06:22.720
You should learn from your grandfather.

06:29.040 --> 06:30.040
I know

06:30.040 --> 06:31.700
that you and Yan Xun are close.

06:31.720 --> 06:33.920
I'll grant you a favor.

06:34.310 --> 06:34.830
Come on.

06:39.680 --> 06:41.240
I'll spare Yan Xun's life.

06:41.310 --> 06:43.510
Whether he survives,

06:43.720 --> 06:45.159
however, depends on

06:45.159 --> 06:47.560
whether you can do this for me.

06:55.520 --> 06:57.920
Qingshan Manor was just following orders—

06:59.070 --> 07:01.000
there was nothing wrong with that.

07:01.360 --> 07:02.120
Back then,

07:03.430 --> 07:05.690
you should've let me die on that platform

07:06.310 --> 07:08.070
with my family.

07:09.360 --> 07:11.020
You shouldn't have spared me.

07:19.360 --> 07:20.960
Sixteen members of my family

07:21.600 --> 07:23.000
died because of you.

07:23.430 --> 07:25.000
Now I'm the only one left.

07:26.070 --> 07:26.870
Do it.

07:33.070 --> 07:34.200
I saved you back then

07:35.159 --> 07:36.560
out of our friendship.

07:37.830 --> 07:39.290
But from this day forward,

07:39.830 --> 07:41.360
we'll go our separate ways.

07:41.510 --> 07:42.800
Our past ties

07:43.950 --> 07:45.360
end here.

08:09.600 --> 08:10.400
Your Majesty.

08:11.360 --> 08:12.600
We just received news

08:12.680 --> 08:14.310
that Jing has led 2,000 soldiers
of the Black Eagle Army

08:14.310 --> 08:15.630
safely into Ximeng.

08:15.920 --> 08:16.630
They've already reached

08:16.630 --> 08:19.490
the mountain hollow
east of the Black River Valley.

08:23.390 --> 08:25.120
Pack up. We set out immediately

08:25.680 --> 08:28.160
for the Black River Valley to meet them.

08:29.040 --> 08:29.430
Yes.

08:29.430 --> 08:29.870
Yes.

09:36.080 --> 09:36.810
How did it go?

09:37.230 --> 09:38.440
That woman was extremely cautious.

09:38.440 --> 09:40.320
She wandered all over the South Market

09:40.320 --> 09:41.440
but didn't do anything noteworthy.

09:41.440 --> 09:42.910
It seems she deliberately
covered her tracks

09:42.910 --> 09:44.370
to shake off any pursuers.

09:44.480 --> 09:45.840
What is this place now?

09:45.960 --> 09:46.630
I don't know.

09:46.630 --> 09:48.790
Nothing can be made out from the outside.

09:48.790 --> 09:49.360
Minglu.

09:49.750 --> 09:51.080
Post two men at the front
and rear entrances

09:51.080 --> 09:53.630
and have the rest seal off this street.

10:40.790 --> 10:42.190
You've finally come.

10:43.000 --> 10:43.720
Who are you?

10:49.040 --> 10:50.590
Haven't we met before?

10:55.640 --> 10:58.280
I am you, and you are me.

10:58.550 --> 10:59.920
I am Chu Qiao.

11:04.510 --> 11:05.910
You're not me.

11:06.150 --> 11:07.000
I am you.

11:07.000 --> 11:08.400
What exactly do you want?

11:08.510 --> 11:09.790
I am you—

11:10.550 --> 11:12.630
the one chosen by the Faceless God,

11:13.000 --> 11:15.440
Queen Ximeng, wielding

11:15.440 --> 11:19.030
supreme authority
over all within her realm.

11:20.030 --> 11:22.030
I'm everything you desire.

11:22.390 --> 11:24.120
It's not that you don't know me,

11:24.120 --> 11:25.980
but that you don't know yourself.

11:26.240 --> 11:27.790
Do you really think

11:28.120 --> 11:30.450
you're freeing the slaves and ending war?

11:30.750 --> 11:32.200
You killed King Ximeng,

11:32.270 --> 11:34.080
overthrew his rule,

11:34.080 --> 11:36.010
and became the new ruler yourself!

11:36.150 --> 11:37.350
Do you really believe

11:37.600 --> 11:39.320
you're saving them?

11:39.510 --> 11:41.440
What exactly are you trying to say?

11:43.310 --> 11:45.190
You're not from Ximeng at all.

11:45.510 --> 11:49.000
What right do you have
to make decisions for them?

11:50.360 --> 11:52.510
You think they need you?

11:54.320 --> 11:55.390
You're wrong.

11:56.870 --> 11:58.630
It's you who needs them.

11:59.870 --> 12:01.510
You're no longer

12:02.080 --> 12:04.360
that humble little slave girl.

12:04.910 --> 12:06.720
You revel in standing above all others—

12:06.720 --> 12:08.920
in being thanked, in being worshipped.

12:08.960 --> 12:10.790
That feeling is power!

12:10.870 --> 12:12.600
You love power!

12:12.600 --> 12:13.530
That's not true!

12:14.630 --> 12:15.560
Don't be afraid.

12:16.200 --> 12:17.440
I'm here to save you.

12:17.870 --> 12:19.480
I'll help you hold on to it

12:20.270 --> 12:21.480
tightly.

12:58.840 --> 13:00.570
Why is it still so quiet inside?

13:01.270 --> 13:02.930
Come on. Let's go in and check.

13:36.360 --> 13:37.120
Lady Chu!

13:41.960 --> 13:43.420
The smell of it is a bit off.

13:45.630 --> 13:46.760
We've been tricked.

14:11.080 --> 14:11.960
Mother!

14:28.360 --> 14:30.600
My child!

14:35.630 --> 14:37.640
You're a witch! Don't come near!

14:37.910 --> 14:40.150
Witch! Stay away!

14:40.870 --> 14:41.960
It's all your fault!

14:41.960 --> 14:42.870
Witch!

14:42.870 --> 14:44.150
Witch!

14:56.320 --> 14:58.240
Give me back my family!

14:59.440 --> 15:00.750
It's her!

15:01.120 --> 15:02.980
-It's the Queen!
-It's the Queen!

15:05.000 --> 15:06.600
She's bewitched the King!

15:06.630 --> 15:07.750
Kill her!

15:08.200 --> 15:09.240
Witch!

15:09.550 --> 15:10.080
Witch!

15:10.080 --> 15:10.910
Kill her!

15:12.240 --> 15:13.500
This is all your fault!

15:15.120 --> 15:15.840
Kill her!

15:16.000 --> 15:16.750
Kill her!

15:18.080 --> 15:19.870
Witch! Witch!

15:21.820 --> 15:23.150
It's all because of you!

15:24.870 --> 15:26.000
Kill her!

15:27.150 --> 15:27.870
Kill her!

15:28.870 --> 15:29.630
Kill her!

15:33.670 --> 15:35.390
-Move aside!
-Move!

15:36.320 --> 15:36.960
Step back!

15:37.360 --> 15:39.030
-Step back!
-All of you, step back!

15:39.030 --> 15:41.030
Kill her! It's all because of her!

15:41.030 --> 15:42.200
We can't let her go!

15:42.200 --> 15:42.910
Kill her! Kill her!

15:42.910 --> 15:43.670
She must pay with her life!

15:43.670 --> 15:44.550
You three,

15:44.550 --> 15:46.270
go tend to the injured civilians first.

15:46.270 --> 15:48.320
Send the severely injured
to the physician's hall at once.

15:48.320 --> 15:50.320
Treat the rest according to the severity
of their injuries.

15:50.320 --> 15:51.720
They may collect medicine
and leave on their own.

15:51.720 --> 15:52.380
-Yes!
-Yes!

15:53.870 --> 15:54.670
My leg!

15:55.670 --> 15:56.360
My leg!

16:01.150 --> 16:01.830
Minglu!

16:02.800 --> 16:03.800
Okay, right away.

16:07.670 --> 16:08.550
Wait, Xiao,

16:08.840 --> 16:10.320
can't you at least
give him some anesthesia?

16:10.320 --> 16:12.850
He's already passed out,
so no need to bother.

16:13.670 --> 16:14.750
Let go of me!

16:15.200 --> 16:17.000
You're in cahoots with that witch!

16:17.000 --> 16:18.200
I don't need your help!

16:18.200 --> 16:19.460
You're badly injured.

16:19.510 --> 16:20.390
If it's left untreated,

16:20.390 --> 16:22.270
you'll lose your whole arm.

16:22.270 --> 16:23.550
Drop the act!

16:23.750 --> 16:25.120
I saw that witch ignite the explosion

16:25.120 --> 16:26.440
in the city with my own eyes.

16:26.440 --> 16:27.360
Not just me,

16:27.360 --> 16:28.750
everyone there

16:28.870 --> 16:29.840
saw it!

16:29.840 --> 16:31.080
-Yes!
-We all saw it!

16:31.080 --> 16:33.000
You're still trying to deceive us?

16:33.000 --> 16:34.870
Right, you still want to lie to us?

16:35.080 --> 16:37.000
Yes, it was the Queen!

16:37.390 --> 16:38.480
Before the explosion,

16:38.480 --> 16:40.240
we all saw her standing right there!

16:40.240 --> 16:40.960
What "Queen"?

16:40.960 --> 16:42.150
-Yes!
-She's a witch!

16:42.150 --> 16:43.600
She's bewitched the King!

16:43.600 --> 16:44.200
It was her!

16:44.200 --> 16:44.790
Yes, it was her!

16:44.790 --> 16:46.480
That's right! She's deceived our King!

16:46.480 --> 16:48.010
-It was her!
-She's a witch!

16:49.270 --> 16:50.080
Witch!

16:50.080 --> 16:51.320
-Witch!
-Witch!

16:53.000 --> 16:54.030
It's all her fault!

16:54.030 --> 16:55.200
She deceived us!

16:55.200 --> 16:56.260
It's all her fault!

16:56.480 --> 16:57.670
We all saw it.

17:00.030 --> 17:00.910
You go over there

17:00.910 --> 17:02.670
and bring the bucket of anesthetic
I prepared.

17:02.670 --> 17:03.790
The whole bucket.

17:05.200 --> 17:06.200
What are you going to do?

17:06.200 --> 17:07.310
To quiet them down

17:07.589 --> 17:09.119
so I can treat their wounds.

17:22.920 --> 17:25.420
[Envoy of Great Yong]

18:03.920 --> 18:04.480
[Chu Qiao, Queen Ximeng, is His Majesty's
long-lost biological daughter.]

18:04.480 --> 18:04.760
[They are bound by blood,
with profound familial ties.]

18:04.760 --> 18:05.040
[In remorse for the princess's years
among the common folk,]

18:05.060 --> 18:05.610
[His Majesty hereby confers upon
Chu Qiao the title of princess]

18:05.610 --> 18:06.170
[and orders her immediate return to
Zhenhuangcheng for reunion.]

18:11.200 --> 18:11.860
Dismissed!

18:17.440 --> 18:19.440
King Ximeng, look carefully.

18:19.750 --> 18:22.030
Our Emperor recently found out by chance

18:22.110 --> 18:23.960
that your queen, Chu Qiao,

18:23.960 --> 18:26.790
is his long-lost biological daughter.

18:26.960 --> 18:29.490
He's specially sent me
to deliver his decree.

18:29.560 --> 18:31.400
First, she is to be granted
the title of princess

18:31.400 --> 18:33.750
and is to return to Zhenhuangcheng
as soon as possible

18:33.750 --> 18:35.590
to reunite with our Emperor.

18:36.110 --> 18:39.000
Second, since Ximeng is
remote and underdeveloped,

18:39.000 --> 18:40.960
and the Princess is of noble birth,

18:40.960 --> 18:42.750
she naturally deserves the highest honor.

18:42.750 --> 18:44.640
Our Emperor has decreed
to grant the Princess

18:44.640 --> 18:46.270
a contingent of the Yong Army,

18:46.270 --> 18:48.730
which is now stationed
outside Ximeng Pass.

18:48.960 --> 18:52.480
As soon as the Princess receives
the imperial investiture decree,

18:52.480 --> 18:54.960
she can lead the army back to Ximeng

18:55.200 --> 18:57.790
to protect herself.

18:58.830 --> 18:59.890
This secret decree

19:00.310 --> 19:02.310
was issued by your Emperor himself?

19:03.880 --> 19:06.200
His Majesty has been unwell recently,

19:06.350 --> 19:08.960
so the Thirteenth Prince is
overseeing state affairs.

19:08.960 --> 19:11.000
Since the secret decree bears
the imperial seal,

19:11.000 --> 19:12.930
it represents His Majesty's will!

19:13.310 --> 19:16.200
So, why bother asking, King Ximeng?

19:19.400 --> 19:20.530
Something's wrong!

19:20.830 --> 19:22.760
Something terrible has happened!

19:23.240 --> 19:24.040
It's serious!

19:24.720 --> 19:26.050
Something's happened!

19:26.790 --> 19:27.590
What's wrong?

19:31.510 --> 19:32.840
What exactly happened?

19:34.310 --> 19:36.510
Lady Chu is now a princess of Great Yong.

19:37.750 --> 19:38.750
-What?
-What?

19:43.110 --> 19:43.920
Wang Shi'er,

19:44.440 --> 19:45.770
what exactly happened?

19:46.160 --> 19:47.750
An envoy from Great Yong just arrived.

19:47.750 --> 19:49.110
He said you are of royal blood

19:49.110 --> 19:52.370
and that they want to confer upon you
the title of princess.

19:54.160 --> 19:55.760
You may not know this, Envoy,

19:56.480 --> 19:58.920
but an accident occurred
in Ximengcheng yesterday.

19:58.920 --> 20:01.750
The Queen is currently in the city
aiding the people.

20:01.750 --> 20:04.810
Why don't you rest here for a while,

20:04.830 --> 20:07.560
and we can discuss this further
when she returns?

20:12.720 --> 20:14.680
By order of the Thirteenth Prince,

20:14.680 --> 20:17.200
I must return immediately
after delivering the secret edict!

20:17.200 --> 20:18.350
I dare not delay!

20:18.550 --> 20:20.210
So I won't intrude any longer!

20:27.030 --> 20:28.440
W-Well... King Ximeng!

20:28.750 --> 20:31.160
Even in wartime,
envoys are not to be harmed!

20:31.160 --> 20:31.830
My Lord,

20:32.310 --> 20:33.070
calm down.

20:34.510 --> 20:35.920
His Majesty

20:36.070 --> 20:37.920
just wants you to get some rest.

20:38.830 --> 20:39.550
Guards!

20:40.240 --> 20:41.070
King Ximeng!

20:41.640 --> 20:43.110
I'm a Great Yong envoy!

20:43.270 --> 20:45.000
How dare you treat me like this?

20:45.000 --> 20:45.800
Take him away.

20:46.790 --> 20:48.160
-Move!
-What are you doing?

20:48.160 --> 20:48.960
King Ximeng!

20:49.110 --> 20:51.200
I'm a Great Yong envoy!

20:51.440 --> 20:53.920
Let go! Let go of me!

20:54.640 --> 20:56.750
I'm an envoy of Great Yong!

20:57.310 --> 20:58.510
Let go of me!

20:58.680 --> 21:00.350
I'm a Great Yong envoy!

21:00.440 --> 21:01.520
Let me go!

21:02.960 --> 21:04.880
You insolent fools!

21:05.030 --> 21:06.070
Let go of me!

21:06.350 --> 21:08.680
I'm a Great Yong envoy!

21:09.960 --> 21:11.480
Let go of me!

21:12.440 --> 21:13.310
Told you.

21:13.480 --> 21:14.720
We've been here for almost half a month

21:14.720 --> 21:16.510
and haven't seen a scrap of meat.

21:16.510 --> 21:18.400
Eating that bran mash all day,

21:18.400 --> 21:20.350
I'm about to turn into bran mash myself.

21:20.350 --> 21:21.280
Tell me about it.

21:21.480 --> 21:22.750
We're just unlucky,

21:22.750 --> 21:24.110
following the Seventh Prince.

21:24.110 --> 21:25.960
We rendered great service
reinforcing Biantang,

21:25.960 --> 21:26.920
and now we're stuck in this dump.

21:26.920 --> 21:27.550
Yeah.

21:27.550 --> 21:29.550
Meanwhile, that useless Thirteenth Prince

21:29.550 --> 21:30.880
is being treated like a treasure
by His Majesty.

21:30.880 --> 21:31.750
Look,

21:31.830 --> 21:33.480
haven't the military achievements
of Great Yong all these years

21:33.480 --> 21:35.160
been won by His Highness on horseback?

21:35.160 --> 21:36.270
Shut up, all of you!

21:37.070 --> 21:38.440
If His Highness hears this,

21:38.440 --> 21:40.900
how many heads do you think
you have to spare?

21:45.480 --> 21:46.030
Chase it!

21:52.680 --> 21:53.080
You...

21:54.480 --> 21:55.010
Chase it!

21:58.750 --> 21:59.960
Got a free sheep.

21:59.960 --> 22:00.790
We can have meat again tonight!

22:00.790 --> 22:01.480
Let go of our sheep!

22:01.480 --> 22:02.110
Put down our sheep!

22:02.110 --> 22:02.830
That is our sheep!

22:02.830 --> 22:03.490
Put it down!

22:03.680 --> 22:04.440
This is our sheep!

22:04.440 --> 22:05.160
You Yong people!

22:05.160 --> 22:07.220
How dare you trespass into our state!

22:07.860 --> 22:09.120
[Great Yan]

22:10.480 --> 22:12.350
All that head and nothing in it?

22:12.350 --> 22:14.430
Did we even cross the border?
Look carefully!

22:14.430 --> 22:15.680
Although you didn't cross the border,

22:15.680 --> 22:17.270
the sheep is in our state, Great Yan!

22:17.270 --> 22:18.270
So this is our sheep!

22:18.270 --> 22:19.070
On what grounds?

22:19.070 --> 22:21.030
This sheep ran over from our country!

22:21.030 --> 22:22.030
It's our sheep!

22:22.030 --> 22:23.790
The sheep ran here on its own!

22:24.110 --> 22:25.880
Whatever land it wanders onto,
that's whose sheep it is!

22:25.880 --> 22:26.310
Right!

22:26.550 --> 22:29.030
Great Yong's soldiers
have trespassed into our territory!

22:29.030 --> 22:29.960
Go inform the general!

22:29.960 --> 22:31.650
What's the big deal
about your general, anyway?

22:31.650 --> 22:33.150
Let's go inform our Seventh Prince!

22:33.150 --> 22:34.830
-Right!
-Let's go inform His Highness!

22:34.830 --> 22:36.360
Let's go tell His Highness!

22:47.920 --> 22:49.640
So it's you, you thief.

22:49.880 --> 22:50.680
"Thief?"

22:51.000 --> 22:52.200
You stole my donkey,

22:52.400 --> 22:54.550
and your soldiers stole our state's sheep.

22:54.550 --> 22:56.720
Like master, like servant.

22:57.240 --> 22:59.170
I sent you the money for the donkey.

22:59.310 --> 23:00.510
I even wrote in my letter

23:00.510 --> 23:01.640
that I was buying it.

23:02.090 --> 23:03.160
You didn't receive the letter?

23:03.160 --> 23:04.500
Taking without asking is stealing!

23:04.500 --> 23:05.510
You wanted to buy it,

23:05.510 --> 23:06.550
but did you ask me first?

23:06.550 --> 23:08.830
You're all crooked intentions
dressed up as righteousness.

23:08.830 --> 23:09.790
I'm not selling that donkey.

23:09.790 --> 23:10.960
Since I've run into you today,

23:10.960 --> 23:13.160
hurry up and bring the donkey back to me.

23:13.310 --> 23:14.310
That donkey...

23:15.030 --> 23:16.560
is left in Zhenhuangcheng.

23:27.070 --> 23:28.400
Where exactly is my donkey?

23:28.400 --> 23:30.110
Don't tell me you already ate it!

23:30.110 --> 23:31.040
Absolutely not.

23:31.480 --> 23:32.510
It really is in Zhenhuangcheng,

23:32.510 --> 23:33.510
alive and well.

23:33.510 --> 23:34.880
If it dies,

23:34.960 --> 23:35.760
I'll kill you!

23:38.350 --> 23:39.550
Put your knives down.

23:39.880 --> 23:41.480
What His Highness said is all true!

23:41.480 --> 23:42.280
That's right.

23:42.400 --> 23:44.880
We've been giving your donkey
the royal treatment.

23:44.880 --> 23:46.210
Waited on hand and foot!

23:46.240 --> 23:48.030
His Highness even found it

23:48.030 --> 23:49.270
a fine mate.

23:49.350 --> 23:52.080
That's right.
It's already had two little foals!

23:54.510 --> 23:55.240
Don't worry.

23:55.590 --> 23:56.480
When I return to Great Yong,

23:56.480 --> 23:58.070
I'll have the donkey sent back to you.

23:58.070 --> 23:59.720
But you'll have to

23:59.720 --> 24:00.850
wait a few more days.

24:04.160 --> 24:05.270
In that case,

24:05.480 --> 24:08.030
I'll take this sheep as interest.

24:08.750 --> 24:09.880
Take the sheep away!

24:10.000 --> 24:10.510
Yes!

24:12.350 --> 24:14.110
Let's go back and roast the sheep!

24:14.110 --> 24:14.790
Let's go!

24:23.350 --> 24:24.350
Wait! Wait!

24:24.680 --> 24:26.410
General Huan hasn't eaten yet!

24:38.310 --> 24:39.110
General Huan.

24:41.070 --> 24:41.640
General?

24:43.680 --> 24:44.640
This is for you.

24:47.240 --> 24:47.790
Wait!

24:49.640 --> 24:52.000
That Great Yong general from earlier...

24:53.350 --> 24:55.160
I heard them call him the Seventh Prince.

24:55.160 --> 24:55.720
Yes.

24:56.310 --> 24:58.350
He's Zhao Che,
the Seventh Prince of Great Yong.

24:58.350 --> 24:59.160
He led troops

24:59.160 --> 25:00.760
against us for quite a while.

25:02.030 --> 25:02.590
Why?

25:03.240 --> 25:04.900
You have a grudge against him?

25:04.960 --> 25:05.640
Yes.

25:06.440 --> 25:08.160
Quite a deep one.

25:08.590 --> 25:10.960
But he seemed pretty nice to you today.

25:11.350 --> 25:12.750
He even gave us the sheep.

25:14.790 --> 25:16.720
That's because he was in the wrong.

25:20.960 --> 25:21.750
Wait for me!

25:23.110 --> 25:23.720
Come on!

25:37.680 --> 25:40.140
Still worried about what happened earlier?

25:40.270 --> 25:42.270
I know you had that envoy locked up

25:42.920 --> 25:45.320
because you feared his words would spread.

25:45.750 --> 25:47.110
But we can't keep him

25:47.550 --> 25:48.720
locked up forever.

25:49.030 --> 25:50.030
Lately,

25:50.350 --> 25:51.000
I've had Yue Shiyi

25:51.000 --> 25:53.200
investigating this Faceless God Sect.

25:53.400 --> 25:55.330
This cult originated in Great Yong

25:55.590 --> 25:58.640
and has been rising in Zhenhuangcheng
over the past three months.

25:58.640 --> 26:01.160
Princess Chun'er was
one of the earliest followers.

26:01.160 --> 26:04.440
Now even the Thirteenth Prince, Zhao Yang,
has joined.

26:05.590 --> 26:07.310
Zhao Chun'er and Zhao Yang?

26:09.160 --> 26:10.350
Whether it's this Faceless God Sect

26:10.350 --> 26:11.950
or today's imperial decree,

26:12.000 --> 26:13.070
both are part of their plot to sow discord

26:13.070 --> 26:14.920
between you and the people of Ximeng.

26:14.920 --> 26:16.780
Ximeng used to be unclaimed land.

26:17.070 --> 26:17.720
Now,

26:18.270 --> 26:20.110
we've built a new realm here.

26:20.550 --> 26:22.830
The people farm,
and the harvests are abundant.

26:22.830 --> 26:24.400
On top of that,
there are black gold mines.

26:24.400 --> 26:26.440
Not only does Yan Xun
want a piece of the pie,

26:26.440 --> 26:29.370
but Great Yong must've been eyeing it
for a long time.

26:29.440 --> 26:30.310
If so,

26:30.480 --> 26:32.790
they must've
set their sights on me long ago.

26:32.790 --> 26:35.990
Then your identity will probably be
even more dangerous.

26:44.720 --> 26:45.960
Since the moment I was chosen

26:45.960 --> 26:47.960
as the heir of Qingshan Manor,

26:48.790 --> 26:50.830
I've lived under constant danger
because of my identity.

26:50.830 --> 26:53.480
Brothers from collateral branches
watched me like hawks,

26:53.480 --> 26:55.310
and at court, serving the emperor
was like living beside a tiger.

26:55.310 --> 26:56.510
Compared to all that,

26:56.960 --> 26:59.550
this is already the best situation
I've ever had.

26:59.550 --> 27:01.480
From when I was still Jing Xiaoliu,

27:01.880 --> 27:04.240
saved by you
from the human hunting ground,

27:04.240 --> 27:06.500
to being able to be with you
like this now—

27:07.200 --> 27:09.800
this too is the best situation
I've ever known.

27:20.480 --> 27:22.750
Did you hear? Queen Ximeng

27:22.750 --> 27:24.550
was never an escaped slave
from Great Yong.

27:24.550 --> 27:27.550
She's actually
the Emperor of Great Yong's daughter.

27:27.680 --> 27:29.280
What's written on the paper?

27:29.880 --> 27:31.350
It's about her background.

27:31.350 --> 27:32.150
It says

27:32.150 --> 27:34.750
the Emperor of Great Yong
deliberately raised her among spies.

27:34.750 --> 27:36.220
She married our King Ximeng

27:36.220 --> 27:37.950
in order to conquer our Ximeng.

27:38.880 --> 27:40.210
Young Master, Lady Chu.

27:40.480 --> 27:41.130
Bad news.

27:41.160 --> 27:41.960
What's wrong?

27:44.270 --> 27:45.960
The news of Lady Chu
being made a princess of Great Yong

27:45.960 --> 27:47.310
has gotten out after all.

27:47.310 --> 27:49.310
Now every commoner outside has a copy.

27:49.310 --> 27:50.920
Those who can read
are passing it around eagerly,

27:50.920 --> 27:52.720
and those who can't
are spreading it by word of mouth.

27:52.720 --> 27:53.720
They're all saying

27:53.720 --> 27:55.350
Lady Chu is a princess of Great Yong,

27:55.350 --> 27:57.440
a spy sent
by the Emperor of Great Yong to Ximeng.

27:57.440 --> 27:58.000
And...

27:58.750 --> 28:00.590
And what? Say it.

28:00.590 --> 28:02.790
Now, the people outside are in an uproar.

28:02.790 --> 28:04.270
They've gathered
at the Wall of Emancipation,

28:04.270 --> 28:06.000
claiming that freeing the slaves was

28:06.000 --> 28:07.000
nothing but a lie,

28:07.000 --> 28:08.930
and they want to tear the wall down.

28:17.270 --> 28:19.240
To hell with the Wall of Emancipation!

28:19.240 --> 28:20.000
Bah!

28:20.230 --> 28:22.420
It was merely a trick
cooked up by Great Yong

28:22.420 --> 28:24.350
and Queen Ximeng together to fool us!

28:24.350 --> 28:25.550
Treating us like idiots!

28:25.550 --> 28:26.510
Yeah! Yeah!

28:26.510 --> 28:28.000
I bet they probably won't

28:28.000 --> 28:29.550
pay us for our work either!

28:29.790 --> 28:31.720
We'd have been better off as slaves
who at least still got fed!

28:31.720 --> 28:34.350
We'll show them what's what!

28:34.510 --> 28:36.110
Show them what we're made of!

28:36.510 --> 28:37.160
Don't go.

28:38.590 --> 28:40.720
They've already been blinded by rumors.

28:40.720 --> 28:41.920
No matter what we say,

28:42.550 --> 28:43.810
they won't believe it.

28:44.000 --> 28:44.720
This wall

28:45.030 --> 28:46.790
is like a monument you built.

28:47.200 --> 28:48.440
It carries immense meaning.

28:48.440 --> 28:49.880
It cannot be torn down like this.

28:49.880 --> 28:52.160
Look, it's King Ximeng and Queen Ximeng!

28:52.160 --> 28:53.360
What "Queen Ximeng"?

28:53.440 --> 28:55.070
She's a princess of Great Yong!

28:55.070 --> 28:56.310
-Liar!
-Liar!

28:56.400 --> 29:00.270
-Liar!
-Liar!

29:00.270 --> 29:01.790
-You're liars!
-Liars!

29:01.790 --> 29:03.160
Big liars! They're liars!

29:03.160 --> 29:04.350
I'm talking about you, liar!

29:04.350 --> 29:05.680
Liars! Liars!

29:05.680 --> 29:06.790
You're liars!

29:06.790 --> 29:09.030
Liars! Just liars!

29:09.200 --> 29:10.790
Liars! Big liars!

29:10.790 --> 29:11.590
Big liars!

29:11.920 --> 29:13.310
What "Queen"? Liar!

29:13.310 --> 29:14.440
All of you, step back!

29:14.440 --> 29:15.640
Step back! Step back!

29:15.790 --> 29:16.400
Lady Chu.

29:16.400 --> 29:16.830
Step back!

29:16.830 --> 29:17.310
Your Majesty.

29:17.310 --> 29:18.030
He Xiao?

29:18.200 --> 29:19.160
Why are you here?

29:20.030 --> 29:22.160
Young Master Zhuge anticipated
there would be unrest here,

29:22.160 --> 29:24.030
so he had Yue Shiyi send me a letter.

29:24.030 --> 29:25.680
Upon receiving it,
I immediately led the Xiuli Army,

29:25.680 --> 29:26.960
traveling day and night to get here.

29:26.960 --> 29:28.110
And yet we were still too late.

29:28.110 --> 29:29.240
How is Biantang now?

29:29.350 --> 29:30.680
Is everything alright?

29:31.030 --> 29:33.560
How are Fang Miaomiao,
Lin Mu, and the others?

29:33.640 --> 29:34.720
Everything is fine in Biantang.

29:34.720 --> 29:35.880
You can rest assured, My Lady.

29:35.880 --> 29:36.680
General Sun

29:37.480 --> 29:38.400
and Grand Secretary Liu

29:38.400 --> 29:40.660
are still expecting me to bring you back.

29:40.830 --> 29:42.560
News has come from Ximeng Pass.

29:42.640 --> 29:44.640
That envoy from Great Yong
was telling the truth.

29:44.640 --> 29:46.510
Great Yong did dispatch an army

29:46.510 --> 29:47.960
to station outside the pass,

29:47.960 --> 29:49.290
claiming to be your army

29:49.790 --> 29:52.350
and demanding
that the guards let them through.

29:52.350 --> 29:53.880
This is only the beginning.

29:54.110 --> 29:56.400
Next, they'll try every means possible

29:56.400 --> 29:57.750
to force us to compromise.

29:57.750 --> 29:58.510
Great Yong

29:58.880 --> 30:00.270
has blockaded the Luo River

30:00.270 --> 30:01.510
and Shuangfeng River

30:01.510 --> 30:02.680
for seven days now.

30:02.830 --> 30:03.960
Those two waterways

30:04.270 --> 30:06.670
are the only routes
for us to go to Biantang.

30:06.960 --> 30:07.550
Exactly.

30:08.160 --> 30:09.880
If we wish to sell our horses

30:09.880 --> 30:11.480
and animal hides in Biantang,

30:11.480 --> 30:13.400
we must pass through those two waterways.

30:13.400 --> 30:14.240
It seems

30:14.640 --> 30:17.000
that making you a princess
was never the true goal—

30:17.000 --> 30:20.000
taking over Ximeng in your name
is their real purpose.

30:32.110 --> 30:32.910
Young Master.

30:37.920 --> 30:38.650
What is this?

30:41.030 --> 30:43.110
It's the list of estates and properties
you secretly purchased

30:43.110 --> 30:45.240
when you were Chief of Qingshan Manor.

30:46.000 --> 30:48.070
Aside from a few used as mission bases,

30:48.070 --> 30:49.800
the rest have been left vacant,

30:50.270 --> 30:51.480
and no one knows about them.

30:51.480 --> 30:53.240
I've written down
the locations of all these properties

30:53.240 --> 30:54.510
along with their deeds.

30:54.510 --> 30:55.400
Take this

30:55.590 --> 30:57.160
and run away with Lady Chu.

30:59.350 --> 31:00.030
Shiyi.

31:03.350 --> 31:05.440
This is the spy tally of Qingshan Manor.

31:05.440 --> 31:07.970
It has the date
I joined the manor carved on it.

31:08.000 --> 31:08.960
When I die,

31:09.480 --> 31:12.140
the date of my death
will be engraved on the back.

31:12.200 --> 31:13.920
Since the day I joined Qingshan Manor,

31:13.920 --> 31:15.270
I've known its rules.

31:16.000 --> 31:16.680
And I know

31:17.240 --> 31:19.510
my life has long since belonged to it,

31:20.000 --> 31:21.200
beyond my own choice.

31:31.110 --> 31:32.510
If I remember correctly,

31:33.160 --> 31:35.090
you were bought by my grandfather,

31:35.960 --> 31:36.890
and your parents

31:37.880 --> 31:39.480
passed away long ago, right?

31:39.720 --> 31:40.200
Yes.

31:41.030 --> 31:42.960
I was born a slave.

31:43.400 --> 31:44.920
If I hadn't joined Qingshan Manor,

31:44.920 --> 31:46.320
I would've died long ago.

31:47.000 --> 31:49.070
I say this to tell you, Young Master,

31:49.880 --> 31:51.680
that everyone in Qingshan Manor

31:51.720 --> 31:54.320
came there
because they had nowhere else to go,

31:54.790 --> 31:56.790
and they know the rules.

31:57.270 --> 31:58.350
If one day

31:59.000 --> 32:01.660
we're implicated
because of you, Young Master,

32:02.030 --> 32:03.480
it won't be your fault.

32:04.070 --> 32:05.800
The true culprit is Great Yong—

32:05.960 --> 32:07.200
the empire that established it

32:07.200 --> 32:09.720
and every emperor
who has controlled it since.

32:09.720 --> 32:10.680
I know

32:11.310 --> 32:12.510
you've always been trying your best

32:12.510 --> 32:13.770
to be a perfect person.

32:14.110 --> 32:15.550
But actually, Young Master,

32:15.550 --> 32:17.480
you don't have to be so hard on yourself.

32:17.480 --> 32:20.080
You're allowed to
live for yourself, for once.

32:48.160 --> 32:49.620
Are you here to comfort me?

32:51.640 --> 32:53.500
I'm just here to bring you a cloak.

32:54.720 --> 32:56.250
Winters in Ximeng are long.

32:56.640 --> 32:57.750
Though Biantang

32:57.750 --> 32:59.350
is already warmed by spring,

32:59.510 --> 33:00.910
up here in the mountains,

33:01.000 --> 33:02.860
the snow hasn't fully melted yet.

33:12.000 --> 33:12.640
Xing,

33:14.440 --> 33:16.240
let's leave this place together

33:16.880 --> 33:18.740
and live a different kind of life.

33:22.240 --> 33:23.400
A different life?

33:24.440 --> 33:24.830
Yes.

33:26.240 --> 33:28.440
I'll no longer
be General Zhuge of Great Yong

33:28.440 --> 33:29.750
or King Ximeng.

33:30.240 --> 33:31.960
And you won't be General Xiuli of Biantang

33:31.960 --> 33:33.620
or the Empress Dowager Xiuli.

33:38.920 --> 33:41.680
We'll just be an ordinary couple,

33:42.110 --> 33:44.590
traveling the world
and living a simple life.

33:44.590 --> 33:45.830
When the weather is fair,

33:45.830 --> 33:48.480
we'll go to Biantang
to admire flowers and lanterns.

33:48.480 --> 33:49.830
During the rainy season,

33:49.830 --> 33:52.360
we can find a place
with mountains and waters,

33:52.440 --> 33:54.170
warm some wine, and roast meat.

33:54.200 --> 33:55.510
When the cold sets in,

33:56.030 --> 33:58.030
we'll travel to the far north
to see the snow-capped peaks.

33:58.030 --> 33:59.350
And if one day we grow tired

33:59.350 --> 34:00.950
and no longer wish to wander,

34:01.110 --> 34:03.240
we'll settle somewhere you love.

34:03.960 --> 34:05.890
We'll open a teahouse or run an inn.

34:07.550 --> 34:09.510
We'll till the land,
find joy in simple things,

34:09.510 --> 34:11.030
and live as we please.

34:14.670 --> 34:16.190
I've never even imagined

34:17.070 --> 34:18.730
the kind of life you describe.

34:21.360 --> 34:23.030
Then start letting yourself

34:23.110 --> 34:24.150
imagine it.

34:24.920 --> 34:26.380
No matter what you choose,

34:26.440 --> 34:27.760
I'll stay by your side.

34:33.230 --> 34:34.110
Well? How is it?

34:34.190 --> 34:35.190
Is she persuaded?

34:35.760 --> 34:37.880
By the looks of it...

34:38.030 --> 34:39.320
she's more or less...

34:39.670 --> 34:41.710
been talked into it, I guess.

34:42.190 --> 34:43.070
So wordy.

34:43.150 --> 34:45.080
Then why aren't you hurrying back?

34:45.280 --> 34:46.110
Back for what?

34:46.510 --> 34:48.770
To pack for your young master, of course.

34:48.800 --> 34:51.000
I need to go prepare for Lady Chu as well.

34:56.110 --> 34:56.909
I'm going too!

34:57.710 --> 35:00.550
Do you know what He Xiao told me today?

35:01.190 --> 35:04.710
He said that rather than endure
the grinding standoff with Great Yong here,

35:04.710 --> 35:07.440
why not go back to Biantang with him?

35:07.920 --> 35:10.670
Biantang could be a home for me as well.

35:12.110 --> 35:13.710
As far back as I can remember,

35:13.760 --> 35:15.490
I was a slave at Qingshan Manor.

35:16.630 --> 35:18.710
I don't know my parents' names,

35:18.710 --> 35:20.400
nor where I truly come from.

35:20.920 --> 35:22.250
Whether it's Biantang,

35:23.190 --> 35:24.590
Great Yong, or Great Yan,

35:25.630 --> 35:27.560
I have no connection to any of them.

35:27.760 --> 35:29.690
I returned to Great Yan with Yan Xun

35:30.400 --> 35:32.530
and then came to Ximeng from Biantang,

35:33.440 --> 35:34.710
all because I believed

35:35.880 --> 35:38.880
there should be a place in this world

35:39.440 --> 35:41.970
where people are not
divided by rank or class,

35:42.030 --> 35:43.440
where justice exists.

35:44.070 --> 35:45.150
Only such a place

35:46.110 --> 35:47.910
can truly be called my homeland.

36:06.550 --> 36:08.590
We'll just be an ordinary couple,

36:08.960 --> 36:11.360
traveling the world, living a simple life.

36:11.670 --> 36:13.070
When the weather is fair,

36:13.440 --> 36:16.370
we'll go to Biantang
to admire flowers and lanterns.

36:16.440 --> 36:17.840
During the rainy season,

36:18.000 --> 36:20.530
we can find a place
with mountains and waters,

36:20.590 --> 36:21.840
warm some wine, and roast meat.

36:21.840 --> 36:23.040
When the cold sets in,

36:23.510 --> 36:24.920
we'll travel to the far north

36:24.920 --> 36:26.580
to see the snow-capped peaks.

36:26.710 --> 36:27.840
And if one day

36:28.400 --> 36:29.130
we grow tired

36:29.150 --> 36:30.750
and no longer wish to wander,

36:30.840 --> 36:32.880
we'll settle somewhere you love.

36:33.480 --> 36:35.410
We'll open a teahouse or run an inn.

36:35.710 --> 36:37.400
We'll till the land,
find joy in simple things,

36:37.400 --> 36:38.880
and live as we please.

36:42.190 --> 36:42.960
Young Master,

36:42.960 --> 36:44.510
we should take these two white fox cloaks.

36:44.510 --> 36:46.640
They'll keep you warm in the far north.

36:47.280 --> 36:50.210
This pair of ivory combs...
We should take these too.

36:50.280 --> 36:52.190
You can use them to comb Lady Chu's hair.

36:52.190 --> 36:53.790
Besides, ivory is valuable.

36:54.230 --> 36:55.510
If we ever fall on hard times,

36:55.510 --> 36:56.920
we can pawn them to get by.

36:59.480 --> 37:01.590
How could our Young Master
ever fall on hard times?

37:01.590 --> 37:03.720
That won't happen. That won't happen.

37:04.960 --> 37:05.590
Shiyi.

37:06.880 --> 37:08.210
No need to pack anymore.

37:33.690 --> 37:34.290
My Lady,

37:34.760 --> 37:36.000
this is clearly a trap

37:36.000 --> 37:37.130
set by the Yong Army.

37:37.800 --> 37:38.600
Execute them!

37:40.000 --> 37:41.000
You dare lie to me?

37:41.110 --> 37:41.670
"Borrow"

37:41.840 --> 37:43.280
is really just another word for "take."

37:43.280 --> 37:44.230
Change direction!

37:44.230 --> 37:45.400
We're heading for Ximeng Pass!

37:45.400 --> 37:47.760
Yue!

37:49.550 --> 37:50.440
Go!

37:50.440 --> 37:50.840
Hurry!

37:51.320 --> 37:52.070
Today,

37:52.630 --> 37:54.190
we'll fight our way out together!
